### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@apiPath = /api/v1/events

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### Get all events
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}

### Get event by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}/1

### Get on-sale events (ordered by show date)
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}/on-sale

### Get events by category (Concerts = 1, Shows = 2, Sports = 3, Exhibitions = 4)
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}/category/1

### Get events by status (ON_SALE, SOLD_OUT, CANCELLED, etc.)
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}/status/ON_SALE

### Create a new event (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Summer Music Festival 2025",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "showDateTimes": [
    "2025-07-15T19:00:00",
    "2025-07-15T22:00:00"
  ],
  "location": "Central Stadium, Bangkok",
  "onSaleDateTime": "2025-06-01T10:00:00",
  "ticketPrice": 1500.00,
  "detail": "A spectacular summer music festival featuring top artists from around the world. Join us for an unforgettable night of music and entertainment.",
  "condition": "Age 18+. No refunds. No outside food or drinks. Subject to terms and conditions.",
  "eventStatus": "ON_SALE",
  "gateOpen": "1 hour before show start"
}

### Create another event - Sports
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Thailand Premier League - Final Match",
  "categoryId": 3,
  "showDateTimes": [
    "2025-08-20T18:00:00"
  ],
  "location": "Rajamangala National Stadium",
  "onSaleDateTime": "2025-07-01T09:00:00",
  "ticketPrice": 800.00,
  "detail": "Watch the championship finals of Thailand Premier League. Exciting match between the top two teams.",
  "condition": "All ages welcome. Stadium rules apply.",
  "eventStatus": "COMING_SOON",
  "gateOpen": "2 hours before match start"
}

### Update an event (Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventStatus": "SOLD_OUT",
  "ticketPrice": 2000.00
}

### Delete an event (Admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}/1

